description: Description: Vibrant hues for spring! This poppy pink kurta with lovely motifs all over, dori on the neckline, lace detailing on the daman is perfect to jazz up a festive look. Pair with a multi-colored shalwar and a contrasting blue hued dupatta Color: Pink Fabric: Cotton Slub Cut: Frock Slip: Thai Silk Slip Included Dupatta: Dupatta Included Trouser: Shalwar Included
